## Stop Conditions

- The task needs a theory that better explains the situation.
- The theory would force a broad rewrite or speculative abstraction.
- The available evidence does not support the chosen framing.

## Response Shape

```text
Theory: [theory concept -> task situation]
Changed: [what changed, if anything]
Verified: [checks run]
Risk: [remaining uncertainty]
```

